<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <!--START BOOTSTRAPのインポート-->
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      integrity="sha384-ggOyR0iXCbMQv3Xipma34MD+dH/1fQ784/j6cY/iJTQUOhcWr7x9JvoRxT2MZw1T"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    />
    <script
      src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.3.1.slim.min.js"
      integrity="sha384-q8i/X+965DzO0rT7abK41JStQIAqVgRVzpbzo5smXKp4YfRvH+8abtTE1Pi6jizo"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>
    <script
      src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/popper.js/1.14.7/umd/popper.min.js"
      integrity="sha384-UO2eT0CpHqdSJQ6hJty5KVphtPhzWj9WO1clHTMGa3JDZwrnQq4sF86dIHNDz0W1"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>
    <script
      src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/js/bootstrap.min.js"
      integrity="sha384-JjSmVgyd0p3pXB1rRibZUAYoIIy6OrQ6VrjIEaFf/nJGzIxFDsf4x0xIM+B07jRM"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>
    <!--END BOOTSTRAPのインポート-->
    <meta
      name="viewport"
      content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no"
    />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div
        class="jumbotron text-white"
        style="background:url(img/reben_wide.jpeg);background-size: cover"
      >
        <h1 class="mb-3">Leben Yokohama Yamate</h1>
        <p>レーベン横浜山手の共有施設の予約用サイトです</p>
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-secondary mt-5">予約情報の確認</h2>
      <p>
        <span class="badge badge-secondary">入力画面</span> >
        <span class="badge badge-danger">確認画面</span> >
        <span class="badge badge-secondary">完了画面</span>
      </p>
      <div class="mb-5">
        <table class="table">
          <tbody>
            <tr>
              <th scope="row">予約日</th>
              <td><%= reserveDate %></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <th scope="row">氏名</th>
              <td><%= name %></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <th scope="row">部屋番号</th>
              <td><%= roomNum %></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <th scope="row">利用人数</th>
              <td><%= memberNum %>人</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <th scope="row">利用用途</th>
              <td><%= reason %></td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
        <form action="complete" method="post" class="form-horizontal">
          <input type="hidden" name="name" value="<%=name%>" />
          <input type="hidden" name="roomNum" value="<%=roomNum%>" />
          <input type="hidden" name="memberNum" value="<%=memberNum%>" />
          <input type="hidden" name="reason" value="<%=reason%>" />
          <input type="hidden" name="reserveDate" value="<%=reserveDate%>" />

          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-sm-offset-2 col-sm-10">
              <a href="/form" class="btn btn-secondary">戻る</a>
              <input
                type="submit"
                name="reserveBtn"
                value="予約を確定する"
                class="btn btn-primary btn-wide"
              />
            </div>
          </div>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
